        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1019429820" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer368750884532490512"><br/>I&apos;m really disappointed. I thought I&apos;d love this, but I didn&apos;t even like it.<br/><br/>The story dragged, it was boring and it irritated me. I skimmed the last half just to get it over and done with.<br/><br/>I didn&apos;t like any of the characters, not even Berenice. I found Frankie obnoxious, and wanted nothing more than to box her ears.<br/><br/>Reading it was a chore!<br/><br/><br/></span>
  <span id="freeText368750884532490512" style="display:none"><br />I'm really disappointed. I thought I'd love this, but I didn't even like it.<br /><br />The story dragged, it was boring and it irritated me. I skimmed the last half just to get it over and done with.<br /><br />I didn't like any of the characters, not even Berenice. I found Frankie obnoxious, and wanted nothing more than to box her ears.<br /><br />Reading it was a chore!<br /><br /><br /></span>
